<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA21">
<l>niṉṟu nilamaṅkai nīrēṟṟu mūvaṭiyāṟ</l>
<l>ceṉṟu ticaiyaḷanta ceṅkaṇmāṟ – keṉṟum</l>
<l>paṭaiyāḻi puḷḷūrti pāmpaṇaiyāṉ pāta</l>
<l>maṭaiyāḻi neñcē yaṟi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Red-eyed Māl who stood [and] lifted the Lady Earth from the water,</l>
<l>who went [and] with three steps measured the directions, approach</l>
<l>the feet of him who always has the discus as a weapon, the bird as [his] vehicle,</l>
<l>the serpent as a bed; immerse yourself, heart, [and] know [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
